Package uni.bielefeld.cmg.sparkhit.io

This package contains different classes for data I/O.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    FileManager
    This is an interface for managing input and output files via different input and output buffers.
    InputFileManager
    This is an interface for managing input files via different input buffers.
    NGSfileUnitBuffer
    This is an interface for managing input NGS (next generation sequencing) files via different input buffers.
    OutputFileManager
    This is an interface for managing output files via different output buffers.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FastqUnitBuffer
    Returns an object for buffering Fastq files.
    ObjectFileInput
    Returns an object for buffering input object files.
    ObjectFileOutput
    Returns an object for buffering output object files.
    ReadFasta
    Returns an object for buffering input fasta files.
    ReadFastq
    Returns an object for buffering input fastq files.
    readInfo
    This is a data structure class.
    TextFileBufferInput
    Returns an object for buffering input files.
    TextFileBufferOutput
    Returns an object for buffering output files.
